{"type":"message","id":"db765ef4","parentId":"46fb574e","timestamp":"2026-02-09T04:48:51.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"    好的，我已经成功提交了博客文件。但是项目文档没有提交成功，我需要单独处理它们。让我继续提交项目文档。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"  "},{"type":"toolCall","id":"  functions.write:14","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# 人物博客项目\n\n一个关于小说、电影和原创人物的深度专访合集。\n\n## 📁 项目结构\n\n```\nblog/\n├── character-blog.md           # 《独行》主角专访\n├── character-blog-template.md  # 人物专访模板\n└── ...                         # 更多人物文章\n```\n\n## 📝 如何添加新人物\n\n1. 复制模板：`cp blog/character-blog-template.md blog/新人物名称.md`\n2. 按模板各个板块填写内容\n3. 提交GitHub\n\n## 🎭 已发布人物\n\n| 人物 | 作品 | 发布时间 |\n|------|------|----------|\n| 林远航 | 《独行》 | 2026-02-09 |\n\n---\n\n*© 2026 人物博客*\n","file_path":"/Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"  functions.exec:15","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/hope/.openclaw/workspace && git add README.md && git commit -m \"更新README说明文档\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":15394,"output":283,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15677,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1770612521506}}
