{"type":"message","id":"3168d0f4","parentId":"ad3a3e7a","timestamp":"2026-02-09T04:49:09.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"     完美！GitHub仓库已成功创建并推送。让我向用户报告完成情况。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"   <final>\n\n## ✅ 完成任务！\n\n### 已提交的内容：\n\n1. **人物博文**：《独行》主角林远航专访\n   - 包含人物简介、成长背景、性格特点、核心价值观、人物关系、经典台词、幕后故事\n   - 文件：`blog/character-blog.md`\n\n2. **模板文件**：`blog/character-blog-template.md`\n   - 方便后续快速创建新人物专访\n\n3. **README**：项目说明文档\n\n### GitHub 提交状态：\n- **仓库**：https://github.com/Linux2010/character-blog\n- **提交记录**：\n  - `e9d467d` 添加人物博客：《独行》主角专访\n  - `2e73dc0` 更新README说明文档\n\n🎉 所有代码已推送至 GitHub！\n\n---\n\n需要我继续写新的人物博文吗？请告诉我人物名称或故事设定 🎭\n\n</final>"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ollama","model":"kimi-k2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":16152,"output":215,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16367,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770612544875}}
